Photo shared by Blvck Paris on June 30, 2021 tagging @casetify, and @casetify_colab. May be an image of phone.

node.text:
We’re GIVING AWAY 2 products from the @black x @casetify drop to celebrate the official release of the exclusive collab! 🎁🏴
—————————
How to participate:
- Comment your favorite collab product 
- Tag a friend
—————————
Winners: @7synnn and @yenamaybe 🖤

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Blvck Paris in Tokyo, Japan with @blvck_paris.jp. May be a black-and-white image of indoor and text that says 'BLVCK PARIS ARIS'.

node.text: Stay tuned for 2 new stores opening in Tokyo after the summer. 🖤🖤🇯🇵 Where would you like to see us next?

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by Blvck Paris on June 23, 2021 tagging @casetify. May be an image of bottle.

node.text: Blvck x CASETiFY limited collection dropping on June 30th. 🖤📱 Link in bio to subscribe to the Blvcklist for early access. 🏴

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Blvck Paris on June 21, 2021. May be an image of 1 person, outdoors and text that says 'BLSCK PARIS'.

node.text: New drop now live. ☄️🖤🏴 Subscribe to the Blvcklist to have early access before we are sold out. 🎩 Link in bio.

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by Blvck Paris on June 10, 2021 tagging @coupculture. May be an image of bottle, indoor and text that says 'COUP BLVCK PARIS'.

node.text: Blvck x Coup Champagne back in stock. 🍾 Comes with a Blvck saber 🔪 Limited quantity. Link in bio. 🖤
